{"id":98,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":98,"title":"Acts 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Peter and John heal a man lame since birth—Peter preaches repentance—He also speaks of the age of restoration preceding the Second Coming—He identifies Christ as the prophet of whom Moses spoke."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.1","order":"03.07.003.12107"},["b","1"],"Now Peter and John went up together into the temple at the hour of prayer,",["i","being"],"the ninth",["i","hour."]],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.2","order":"03.07.003.12108"},["b","2"],"And a certain man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lame"],"from his mother’s womb was carried, whom they laid daily at the gate of the temple which is called Beautiful, to ask alms of them that entered into the temple;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.3","order":"03.07.003.12109"},["b","3"],"Who seeing Peter and John about to go into the temple asked an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"alms"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.4","order":"03.07.003.12110"},["b","4"],"And Peter, fastening his eyes upon him with John, said, Look on us."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.5","order":"03.07.003.12111"},["b","5"],"And he gave heed unto them, expecting to receive something of them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.6","order":"03.07.003.12112"},["b","6"],"Then Peter said, Silver and gold have I none; but such as I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"give"],"I thee: In the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"name"],"of Jesus Christ of Nazareth rise up and walk."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.7","order":"03.07.003.12113"},["b","7"],"And he took him by the right hand, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"lifted"],["i","him"],"up: and immediately his feet and ankle bones received strength."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.8","order":"03.07.003.12114"},["b","8"],"And he leaping up stood, and walked, and entered with them into the temple, walking, and leaping, and praising God."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.9","order":"03.07.003.12115"},["b","9"],"And all the people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"saw"],"him walking and praising God:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.10","order":"03.07.003.12116"},["b","10"],"And they knew that it was he which sat for alms at the Beautiful gate of the temple: and they were filled with wonder and amazement at that which had happened unto him."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.11","order":"03.07.003.12117"},["b","11"],"And as the lame man which was healed held Peter and John, all the people ran together unto them in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"porch"],"that is called Solomon’s, greatly wondering."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.12","order":"03.07.003.12118"},["b","12"],"¶And when Peter saw",["i","it,"],"he answered unto the people, Ye men of Israel, why marvel ye at this? or why look ye so earnestly on us, as though by our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"own"],"power or holiness we had made this man to walk?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.13","order":"03.07.003.12119"},["b","13"],"The God of Abraham, and of Isaac, and of Jacob, the God of our fathers, hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"glorified"],"his Son Jesus; whom ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"delivered up"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"denied"],"him in the presence of Pilate, when he was determined to let",["i","him"],"go."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.14","order":"03.07.003.12120"},["b","14"],"But ye denied the Holy One and the Just, and desired a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"murderer"],"to be granted unto you;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.15","order":"03.07.003.12121"},["b","15"],"And killed the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Prince"],"of life, whom God hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"raised"],"from the dead; whereof we are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"witnesses"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.16","order":"03.07.003.12122"},["b","16"],"And his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"name"],"through faith in his name hath made this man strong, whom ye see and know: yea, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"faith"],"which is by him hath given him this perfect soundness in the presence of you all."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.17","order":"03.07.003.12123"},["b","17"],"And now, brethren,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"I"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"wot"],"that through",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"ignorance"],"ye did",["i","it,"],"as",["i","did"],"also your rulers."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.18","order":"03.07.003.12124"},["b","18"],"But those things, which God before had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"shewed"],"by the mouth of all his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"prophets"],", that Christ should",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"suffer"],", he hath so fulfilled."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.19","order":"03.07.003.12125"},["b","19"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Repent"],"ye therefore, and be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"converted"],", that your sins may be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"blotted out"],", when the times of refreshing shall come from the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"presence"],"of the Lord;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.20","order":"03.07.003.12126"},["b","20"],"And he shall send",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Jesus Christ"],", which before was preached unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"you"],":"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.21","order":"03.07.003.12127"},["b","21"],"Whom the heaven must receive until the times of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"restitution"],"of all things, which God hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"spoken"],"by the mouth of all his holy prophets since the world began."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.22","order":"03.07.003.12128"},["b","22"],"For Moses truly said unto the fathers, A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prophet"],"shall the Lord your God raise up unto you of your brethren, like unto me; him shall ye hear in all things whatsoever he shall say unto you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.23","order":"03.07.003.12129"},["b","23"],"And it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"every soul, which will not hear that prophet, shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"destroyed"],"from among the people."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.24","order":"03.07.003.12130"},["b","24"],"Yea, and all the prophets from Samuel and those that follow after, as many as have spoken, have likewise",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"foretold"],"of these days."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.25","order":"03.07.003.12131"},["b","25"],"Ye are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"children"],"of the prophets, and of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"covenant"],"which God made with our fathers, saying unto Abraham, And in thy seed shall all the kindreds of the earth be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"blessed"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.26","order":"03.07.003.12132"},["b","26"],"Unto you first God, having raised up his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Son"],"Jesus, sent him to bless you, in turning away every one of you from his iniquities."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.2a","order":"03.07.003.12133"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/14.8.8-10"},"Acts 14:8 (8–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.3a","order":"03.07.003.12135"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/almsgiving"},"TG Almsgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.6a","order":"03.07.003.12137"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.6b","order":"03.07.003.12139"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.10"},"Acts 4:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.6"},"Jacob 4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/8.1"},"3 Ne. 8:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.7a","order":"03.07.003.12141"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9.27"},"Mark 9:27"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.9a","order":"03.07.003.12143"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.16"},"Acts 4:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.11a","order":"03.07.003.12145"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.3"},"1 Kgs. 6:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/10.23"},"John 10:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.12a","order":"03.07.003.12147"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.16"},"Gen. 41:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.30"},"Dan. 2:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.13a","order":"03.07.003.12149"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.14"},"John 16:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.21.17-21"},"1 Pet. 1:21 (17–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.13b","order":"03.07.003.12151"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.20"},"Matt. 27:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.28"},"Acts 13:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.13c","order":"03.07.003.12153"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.6"},"John 19:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.14a","order":"03.07.003.12155"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/23.25.17-19,25"},"Luke 23:25 (17–19, 25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.15a","order":"03.07.003.12157"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.15b","order":"03.07.003.12159"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.40"},"Acts 10:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.15c","order":"03.07.003.12161"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.16a","order":"03.07.003.12163"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.16b","order":"03.07.003.12165"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.17a","order":"03.07.003.12167"},["b","17a"],["span.small","JST"],"Acts 3:17 … I",["i","know"],"that through ignorance ye",["i","have done this,"],"as also your rulers."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.17b","order":"03.07.003.12169"},["b","17b"],["span.small","OR"],"know."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.17c","order":"03.07.003.12171"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.21"},"D&C 6:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.18a","order":"03.07.003.12173"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/foreordination"},"TG Foreordination"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.18b","order":"03.07.003.12175"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.27"},"Luke 24:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.23"},"Acts 28:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/18.36"},"Alma 18:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.18c","order":"03.07.003.12177"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.3"},"1 Cor. 15:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.19a","order":"03.07.003.12179"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.19b","order":"03.07.003.12181"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.19c","order":"03.07.003.12183"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/51.1"},"Ps. 51:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.30"},"Mosiah 26:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.14.11-15,21"},"Alma 5:14 (11–15, 21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.19d","order":"03.07.003.12185"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.20a","order":"03.07.003.12187"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.20b","order":"03.07.003.12189"},["b","20b"],["span.small","JST"],"Acts 3:20 … you,",["i","whom ye have crucified;"]],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.21a","order":"03.07.003.12191"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/restoration-of-the-gospel"},"Restoration of the Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.21b","order":"03.07.003.12193"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.22a","order":"03.07.003.12195"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.15.15-19"},"Deut. 18:15 (15–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.37"},"Acts 7:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.20.20-22"},"1 Ne. 22:20 (20–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.40"},"JS—H 1:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.23a","order":"03.07.003.12197"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.14.14-16"},"D&C 1:14 (14–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.63"},"133:63"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.24a","order":"03.07.003.12199"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.25a","order":"03.07.003.12201"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.25b","order":"03.07.003.12203"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-early-saints"},"Mission of Early Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.25c","order":"03.07.003.12205"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.26a","order":"03.07.003.12207"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],"."]]}
